   "endLine": 515,
   "source": "<ROUTINE EASEL-F ()\n\t<COND (<VERB? TAKE MOVE>\n\t       <TELL\n\"Jill doesn't like you fooling with her painting and drawing stuff.\" CR>)\n\t      (<VERB? EXAMINE>\n\t       <EASEL-DESC T>)>>"
