   "source": "<ROUTINE SINK-F ()\n\t <COND (<AND <VERB? PUT>\n\t\t     <PRSI? ,SINK>>\n\t\t<TELL \"That's a dumb place for\">\n\t\t<ARTICLE ,PRSO>\n\t\t<TELL \".\" CR>)\n\t       (<VERB? EXAMINE LOOK-INSIDE>\n\t\t<COND (<AND <EQUAL? ,HERE ,KITCHEN>\n\t\t     \t    <EQUAL? ,JILL-COUNTER 7>>\n\t\t       <TELL \"The sink is filled with suds.\" CR>)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <TELL \"The sink is empty.\" CR>)>)\n\t       (<VERB? TURN ON OFF>\n\t\t<PERFORM ,PRSA ,WATER>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>>"
