   "source": "<ROUTINE INK-BLOT (\"AUX\" (X 12) (Y 5) (CNT 4) SIDE-OFFSET CENTER-OFFSET CHAR)\n\t <BUFOUT <>>\n\t <SCREEN ,S-WINDOW>\n\t <SET CENTER-OFFSET <RANDOM 6>>\n\t <SET SIDE-OFFSET <RANDOM <- 16 .CENTER-OFFSET>>>\n\t <SET X <+ 22 .SIDE-OFFSET>>\n\t <SET CHAR <RANDOM 3>> ;\"1 = blanks, 2 = x's, 3 = angle brackets\"\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <INVERSE-LINE .CNT T>\n\t\t <SET CNT <+ .CNT 1>>\n\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? .CNT 19>\n\t\t\t<RETURN>)>>\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .CHAR 2 3> ;\"not blanks\"\n\t\t<HLIGHT 1>)>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t\t <CURSET .Y .X>\n\t\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? .CHAR 1>\n\t\t\t \t<TELL \" \">)\n\t\t\t       (<EQUAL? .CHAR 2>\n\t\t\t\t<TELL \"X\">)\n\t\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t\t<TELL \">\">)>\n\t\t\t <CURSET .Y <- 81 .X>>\n\t\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? .CHAR 1>\n\t\t\t \t<TELL \" \">)\n\t\t\t       (<EQUAL? .CHAR 2>\n\t\t\t\t<TELL \"X\">)\n\t\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t\t<TELL \"<\">)>\n\t\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? .X <- 40 .CENTER-OFFSET>>\n\t\t\t\t<RETURN>)\n\t\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t\t<SET X <+ .X 1>>)>>\n\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? .Y 17>\n\t\t\t<RETURN>)\n\t\t       (T\n\t\t\t<COND (<PROB 40>\n\t\t\t       <SET SIDE-OFFSET <+ .SIDE-OFFSET <RANDOM 3>>>)\n\t\t\t      (<PROB 67>\n\t\t\t       <SET SIDE-OFFSET <- .SIDE-OFFSET <RANDOM 3>>>)>\n\t\t\t<COND (<PROB 40>\n\t\t\t       <SET CENTER-OFFSET\n\t\t\t\t    <- .CENTER-OFFSET <RANDOM 2>>>)\n\t\t\t      (<PROB 67>\n\t\t\t       <SET CENTER-OFFSET\n\t\t\t\t    <+ .CENTER-OFFSET <RANDOM 2>>>)>\n\t\t\t<COND (<L? .SIDE-OFFSET 0>\n\t\t\t       <SET SIDE-OFFSET 1>)>\n\t\t\t<COND (<L? .CENTER-OFFSET 0>\n\t\t\t       <SET CENTER-OFFSET 0>)>\n\t\t\t<COND (<G? <+ .SIDE-OFFSET .CENTER-OFFSET> 18>\n\t\t\t       <SET CENTER-OFFSET <- .CENTER-OFFSET 1>>\n\t\t\t       <SET SIDE-OFFSET <- 18 .CENTER-OFFSET>>)>\n\t\t\t<SET X <+ 22 .SIDE-OFFSET>>\n\t\t\t<SET Y <+ .Y 1>>)>>\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .CHAR 2 3> ;\"blanks\"\n\t\t<HLIGHT 0>)>\n\t <SCREEN ,S-TEXT>\n\t <BUFOUT T>>"
