   "source": "<ROUTINE COFFEE-F ()\n\t <COND (<VERB? BUY>\n\t\t<COND (<IN-RESTAURANT?>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"Coffee with a meal is a custom that went out of style decades ago!\" CR>)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <CANT-BUY ,COFFEE>)>)>>"
