   "source": "<ROUTINE QUITE-NEARLY (YEAR1 YEAR2 VAR)\n\t <TELL \"quite enough from \" N .YEAR1 \" or \">\n\t <COND (.VAR\n\t\t<TELL \"anywhere near enough\">)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL \"anything\">)>\n\t <TELL \" from \" N .YEAR2>>"
