  "2041-CITY-NOISES": {
   "name": "2041-CITY-NOISES",
   "kind": "global",
   "file": "rockvil.zil",
   "line": 10486,
   "value": "<LTABLE 0 \"A swirling wind catches a yellowed newspaper page, and blows it upward,\nout of sight.\" \"The ground shakes as a huge truck rumbles down the street.\" \"You are startled as a taxi horn blares nearby.\" \"A skycopter drones by far overhead and disappears into the distance.\" \"Across the street, two policemen are frisking a youth. As you watch, they\nusher the youth into a waiting car and fly off.\" \"A car alarm shrieks momentarily, then trails off into merciful silence.\" \"A stranger bumps against you, mumbles an apology, and is swallowed by\nthe crowds.\" \"A man with a shaved head asks your views on some obscure religious point,\nthen wanders off into the crowds.\">"
  },
  "2051-CITY-NOISES": {
   "name": "2051-CITY-NOISES",
   "kind": "global",
   "file": "rockvil.zil",
   "line": 10502,
   "value": "<LTABLE 0 \"A swirling wind catches a yellowed newspaper page, and blows it upward,\nout of sight.\" \"A panhandler is working his way towards you, but misses you in the crowds.\" \"A dog runs up to you, barking, then vanishes into the crowds.\" \"A squeal of rubber against asphalt announces a near-collision between\ntwo road vehicles.\" \"Two youths wander past carrying loud porta-stereos.\" \"A policeman strolls past, nonchalantly swinging his club.\" \"A distant siren pierces the steady background noise of the city streets.\" \"A stranger bumps against you, mumbles an apology, and is swallowed by\nthe crowds.\">"
  },
  "2061-CITY-NOISES": {
   "name": "2061-CITY-NOISES",
   "kind": "global",
   "file": "rockvil.zil",
   "line": 10517,
   "value": "<LTABLE 0 \"A distant siren pierces the steady background noise of the city streets.\" \"A police van pulls up, and two policemen load a sleeping drunk into the back.\" \"A pregnant woman walks past you, sobbing quietly. You turn, but she is gone,\nswallowed up by the crowds.\" \"A BSF patrol is moving down the block, searching people indiscriminately.\nFortunately, they pass by without stopping you.\" \"A change in the wind brings you a sudden odor of something rotting. A moment\nlater, the odor is gone.\" \"A siren wails with increasing intensity, but then recedes without ever\nrevealing its source.\" \"A sharp crack, like a distant pistol shot, echoes among the buildings.\" \"A distant splintering explosion could only be the sound of another\nskycar crash.\">"
  },
  "2071-CITY-NOISES": {
   "name": "2071-CITY-NOISES",
   "kind": "global",
   "file": "rockvil.zil",
   "line": 10534,
   "value": "<LTABLE 0 \"A sudden gust of wind blows some dust and paper around.\" \"A thin teenager passes you, kicking a dented tin can.\" \"A BSF patrol is moving down the block, searching people indiscriminately.\nFortunately, they pass by without stopping you.\" \"A Church Police Paddywagon coasts slowly down the street, stopping\nhere and there to take someone prisoner.\" \"An ugly mob bearing signs and banners with Church symbols, possibly looking\nfor a lynching victim, appears down the street. You begin looking for a\nhiding place, but fortunately the mob turns onto an adjoining street. You\nstand frozen for a minute as the sounds from the mob recede.\" \"Out of the corner of your eye, you glimpse something that looks like a\npanhandler being dragged into an alley, but when you turn, you see nothing.\" \"A woman dressed in gauzy red fabrics, quite obviously a prostitute, enters\na building with a man garbed in Church robes.\" \"A scream comes from a nearby building, but before you can even determine\nthe direction, it has stopped.\">"
  },
